#. Tag: title
#: symbols.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbols"
msgstr "Simboli"

#. Tag: para
#: symbols.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Symbols are created as QPainterPath objects with additional information "
"defining attributes of the path. A QPainterPath is made up of sub paths such "
"as rectangles, ellipses or chains of lines and bezier curves. The paths may "
"intersect each other forming complex shapes."
msgstr ""
"Simboli so ustvarjeni kot predmeti QPainterPath z dodatnimi informacijami, "
"ki definirajo atribute poti. QPainterPath je sestavljen iz podpoti, kot so "
"pravokotniki, elipse ali verige črt in Bezierjeve krivulje. Poti se lahko "
"sekajo in tvorijo kompleksne oblike."

#. Tag: para
#: symbols.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The symbol may be filled using either the winding option which will fill the "
"entire path, or the odd even option which fill alternate sections of the "
"path."
msgstr ""
"Simbol se lahko zapolni bodisi z možnostjo vijuganja, ki zapolni celotno "
"pot, bodisi z možnostjo liho sodega polnjenja nadomestnih delov poti."

#. Tag: para
#: symbols.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the path is not filled, the outline will have a defined line width, end "
"cap type and line join type."
msgstr ""
"Če pot ni zapolnjena, bo imel obris definirano širino črte, vrsto končne "
"kapice in vrsto spoja črte."

#. Tag: para
#: symbols.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the QPainterPath documentation for more detail."
msgstr "Za več podrobnosti glejte dokumentacijo QPainterPath."
